    "title": "Job Opening Hotel Manager at Wilderness Lodges India",
    "description": "We at Wilderness Lodges India are looking for an experienced Hotel Manager based out of Nagpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Wilderness Lodges India:\nWilderness Lodges India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wilderness Lodges India!",
